#31 a week of husband bento boxes 

[ Contents ] 

🍱Tuesday / Prawn featuring lotus root

🍱Wednesday / Eel and egg rolls, fried garlic shishito 

🌠Thursday dinner / Deep fried oyster, Milk soup with Japanese sweet potato, Tartar sause

🍱Friday / Shrimp & pork fried Udon noodles 

🍱Saturday / Fried quail egg skewers, simmered pork and potatoes
